      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·邶風·018.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">新臺.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>新臺有泚，河水瀰瀰，燕婉之求，蘧篨不鮮。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Fresh and bright is the New Tower,
On the waters of the Ho, wide and deep.
A pleasant, genial mate she sought,
And has got this vicious bloated mass!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
