      <prop type="x-translation-ref">新臺.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>新臺有洒，河水浼浼，燕婉之求，蘧篨不殄。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Lofty is the New Tower,
On the waters of the Ho, flowing still.
A pleasant, genial mate she sought,
And has got this vicious bloated mass!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
