      <prop type="x-translation-ref">新臺.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>魚網之設，鴻則離之，燕婉之求，得此戚施。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It was a fish net that was set,
And a goose has fallen into it.
A pleasant, genial mate she sought,
And she has got this hunchback.</seg>
      </tuv>
